            <h2>Key impact: turned packages from hidden, provider-specific upsells into a scalable, contextual discovery mechanism.
            </h2>
            <h4 class="textItalic fontWeight100 greyBg400 greyBg100 border-radius paddingXS">👉 Key impact: packages become part of decision-making, not optional browsing
            </h4>
            <h4 class="textItalic fontWeight100 greyBg400 greyBg100 border-radius paddingXS">👉 Key impact: Resolved a structural conflict between browsing-first UX and provider-dependent bundles.</h4>
            <h4 class="textItalic fontWeight100 greyBg400 greyBg100 border-radius paddingXS">👉 Key impact: Made bundles discoverable and actionable within item-level browsing
